MoneyPerClass is a field that will be used for mark command to determine by how much
the money should increase when the student is marked as present for one particular
class.

As pointed out in earlier conversation, `moneyPerClass` has been refactored to
`ratesPerClass` for natural variable naming.

The Phone and NokPhone number have been specified to have fixed 8-digit long
and start with 6, 8, or 9. This commit has enforced this constraint into the code.
